Package fr.sorbonne_u.cps.replication.examples.components

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    The class Client implements a test client of a replication service.
    ConstantServer
    The class ConstantServer implements a server component that returns a constant result for any given parameter.
    MonitoredServer
    The class MonitoredServer implements a request server that monitors its request queue size and notify a dispatcher that selects servers to dispatch them request depending on their queue sizes.
    MonitoredServer.MonitoredServerExecutorServiceFactory
    The class MonitoredServerExecutorServiceFactory implements the executor service factory that will be used to create the pool of threads used to executed the requests on this server.
    MonitoredServer.SizeChange
    The class SizeChange records a size change in the request queue with the time at which this change happen.
    RandomServer
    The class RandomServer implements a server component that returns a random result for any given parameter.
    Server
    The class Server implements a server component that returns a customized result for any given parameter.
